{
  "id": "adv_card_ski_13_01",
  "title": "白石沙季 1話 うぅ、意地悪です",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_church-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "church-00-night",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_01-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "この証拠品、何か違和感がありますね\nおそらく、持ち主は別の方ではないでしょうか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_church-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "church-00-night",
      "startTime": 9.7989343007
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_01-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "いえ、あくまで私の浅い考えですから。もしもこれが\n解決に繋がるのなら、私の力というよりも",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.257728828,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_church-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "church-00-night",
      "startTime": 20.0726078669
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_01-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "――神のお導きかもしれませんね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.0726078669,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3885.9643776000007,
          "startTime": 23.9585722445
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_church-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "church-00-night",
      "startTime": 23.7252384025
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "撮影お疲れ様、沙季。いい演技だったぞ\nまるで映画の中に入り込んだようだったな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_church-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "church-00-night",
      "startTime": 32.2919055778
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_01-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございます。これも、監督や共演者の方々が\nリードしてくれたおかげです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.3196034953,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_church-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "church-00-night",
      "startTime": 39.723515717
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "洞察力に優れたシスターが現場に行かずに\n事件を解決するミステリー物か",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "うん、やはりこういう役は沙季に合うな\n監督さんからの評価もいいし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_church-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "church-00-night",
      "startTime": 51.723515717
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_01-ski005.m4a",
      "text": "あまり褒められると照れてしまうのですが……\n自分なりに、努力を重ねた甲斐がありました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_church-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "church-00-night",
      "startTime": 58.6063954827
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_01-ski006.m4a",
      "text": "主演だなんて貴重な経験ですし、クランクアップまで\nどれだけ成長出来ているのか、自分でも楽しみです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.4720511176,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 18094.6155491,
          "startTime": 80.5666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 67.589955409
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "（それから数ヶ月後、沙季は抜群の演技力で）\n（見事に映画をクランクアップさせたのだが……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……映画の撮影が無事に終わったのは良かったが\nまさかこんなことを提案されるとはな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3339.9554089999983,
          "startTime": 84.339955409
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_01-ski007.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様です。この前うかがった\n映画の宣伝用に出演する番組の件ですが――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "うわぁ！？　さ、沙季！\nすまない、資料を読んでいて気付かなかったよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.5666651408,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_01-ski008.m4a",
      "text": "……？　いえ、大丈夫ですけど\nもしかしてそれが、例の番組についての資料ですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.1333343506,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 8866.662089100004,
          "startTime": 110.9999964397
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 11133.3277385,
          "startTime": 113.2666620891
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "あ、あぁ。ちょうど今日資料が届いたんだ\nこれ……じゃなくて、こっちが沙季のだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.9999964397,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4468.891055900002,
          "startTime": 115.4688874956
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_01-ski009.m4a",
      "text": "拝見しますね。ふむふむ……\nえっ？　心霊番組に決まったんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.7059821655,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_01-ski010.m4a",
      "text": "ホラー映画に出るなら分かりますけど\n私が出演する映画はミステリー物ですよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.6082137377,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "あー、それはだな……えっと、千紗がレギュラーの\n番組だから、姉妹の共演を狙ったんだと思うぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.6333328248,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_01-ski011.m4a",
      "text": "なるほど……？　少し引っかかりますが\nそういう需要を狙うこともある、かも……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 144.4666661581,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_01-ski012.m4a",
      "text": "とにかく、私が心霊ロケを行い\nそのVTRを千紗やスタジオの方々が観るのですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 152.2333328248,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "その認識で合っているよ\nちなみに、沙季はこういうの大丈夫なのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 158.9999994915,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_01-ski013.m4a",
      "text": "得意、とは言えませんが……大丈夫です\n千紗と一緒にホラー映画を観たりもしますから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 166.6333328248,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_01-ski014.m4a",
      "text": "それに私は、幽霊のことはあまり信じていないんです\n非科学的ですし、霊感なども持ち合わせてはいないので",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 174.6333328248,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "幽霊を信じていない、か……\n俺も昔はそう思っていたなぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 182.8000025433,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_01-ski015.m4a",
      "text": "きゅ、急に思わせぶりなこと言わないで下さい\n信じてしまいそうになります",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 189.2333409628,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "信じてもいいと思うけどな\n案外、沙季のすぐ近くにいるかもしれないぞ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 194.7000076295,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_13_01-ski016.m4a",
      "text": "近くって……\nうぅ、意地悪です。私を怖がらせたいんですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 200.088547269,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
